    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "兰扎卜说起了当年来到\\n火焰都市巴尔加海姆时的回忆。\\n在巴尔加海姆，人人都有机会出人头地。\\n年轻人野心膨胀，\\n踩着友人向上爬的残酷竞争司空见惯。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "咕噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "唔噢……\\n不好，我的斧子！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "喂，大叔！\\n你行不行啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "没事，我还有其它武器呢。\\n看招，兰扎卜指虎重击！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽",
            "context": "咕噢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "可别小看了我这千锤百炼的身体！\\n来互相伤害啊，噢啦噢啦噢啦！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "好厉害……徒手和魔兽搏斗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "最后一击还是得用斧子啊。\\n喝啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "呦～你那超乎常人的体格\\n还真厉害啊，大叔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "怎么才能锻炼到那种程度啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "哈哈，我只是作为佣兵\\n努力活下来而已。\\n不知不觉间就成这样了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "努力活下来、吃顿好的。\\n变得强大的理由\\n其实出乎意料地单纯。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "诶……那么严苛的活法，\\n我可办不到。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "有没有什么更轻松点的\\n变强方法啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "虽然算不上轻松，但有一个\\n比想着美餐一顿更管用的方法。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "我是在某个城市学到那个方法的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "某个城市？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "给我好好上了一课的，\\n就是火焰都市巴尔加海姆。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "那里的家伙们……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "telop",
            "context": "\\n火焰都市巴尔加海姆\\n小巷中\\n \\n ",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120108_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "年轻人",
            "context": "嘿呀！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "（呃，这一击是怎么回事！？\\n体型瘦小却有如此重击……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "（本来只想小打小闹一下，\\n但这家伙……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "你这家伙，有两下子嘛。\\n是在哪里学过剑术？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120108_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "年轻人",
            "context": "哪有那么高级！\\n谁有空学那玩意儿。不过！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120108_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "年轻人",
            "context": "就算是我这种人，只要每天坚持挥剑，\\n总有一天能进骑士团……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喂喂，说什么傻话呢。\\n只有被选上的人才能进骑士团吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "像你这种街上的三流小混混，\\n再怎么逞能也不可能……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120108_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "年轻人",
            "context": "没这回事！在这里就有可能，\\n在巴尔加海姆的话就有可能！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120108_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "年轻人",
            "context": "所以我……要打倒你！\\n可不能在这里输掉。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "（这家伙的眼神怎么回事……\\n也不像是中了魔法，\\n但看起来完全疯了……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "（为什么他的眼神充满光芒？\\n到底是什么让这家伙如此……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "（后来离开那个城市的时候，偶然听到了\\n领主的演讲……我终于明白了。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "（明白了那个小混混\\n会那么拼命战斗的理由……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "巴尔加海姆的市民们，听好了！\\n我赐予你们所有人梦想。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "无论出身贵贱，皆有机会达成的梦想。\\n磨炼自身，出人头地。\\n无论以什么形式！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "精进武艺吧！汲取知识吧！掌握兵法吧！\\n切勿安于现状。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "与友人竞争，直到其中一方倒下。\\n生存下来的人就是新的友人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "出人头地后，任你予取予求。\\n但是，无所作为之辈只有死路一条。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "这就是巴尔加海姆唯一的规矩。\\n我身为王族，\\n赐予你们所有人的梦想！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "无论什么形式……\\n只要出人头地吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "没错，那座城市教会了我，\\n最能让人变强的就是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "梦想。\\n而且，耀眼得露骨……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "视死如归般追逐梦想之人的一击\\n会无比沉重有力，\\n比任何魔兽都可怕。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "可、可是，梦想不该是那样吧？\\n应该是更开心的感觉才对！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "梦想本来就是五颜六色的啊。简单来说，\\n你说的那种是玫瑰色。但是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "这世上也有赴汤蹈火、奋不顾身的梦想。\\n殒身不恤也要抓住那种梦想的人……\\n一定很强大。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "只有那种家伙才能生存下来的城市，\\n简直就是人间地狱啊。不过……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "他们大概不会察觉吧。\\n使人变得强大、\\n使人失去理智的，都是梦想。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_03_1046",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}